item.title: predicting my natural gas consumption
item.description: It’s been a while since I posted on this blog. That was mainly due to the confinement in the covid-19 pandemic. And it’s a promise, this is the last time I will mention the virus. Let’s get away from all that and look at energy consumption and global warming instead. That will lift our spirits! Here are the packages I need to attach.
